## Common Improvements

| Weak Pattern | Strong Pattern | Example |
|--------------|----------------|---------|
| "Fix the bug" | "Fix the bug in [file] where [symptom]. The expected behavior is [X]." | Adds location, symptom, expected outcome |
| "Make it better" | "Improve [specific aspect] by [specific action]. Success criteria: [X]." | Adds measurable goal |
| "Help me with X" | "I need to [goal]. Current state: [X]. Constraints: [Y]. Suggest approach." | Adds context and constraints |
| "Do the thing we discussed" | "Implement [specific feature] as outlined in [file/previous discussion point]." | Adds explicit reference |
| "Update the docs" | "Update [specific doc] to reflect [specific change]. Match existing style." | Adds scope and style guidance |

